Description: Deep Moisturizing Treatment Foot Hydration Socks (16ml)Features:Get results in 30 minutes,Healthy, youthful and soft skin,Enriched with botanical extracts and antioxidants,Non messy and non sticky,pH balanced to 6.5.Free from Paraben, Sulphates, Phthalates, Heavy Metals, Alcohol, Artificial Color and Fragrances.Description: Deep Moisturizing Treatment- Foot Hydration Socks contains a nutrient and moisture rich solution ideal for those who look forward to pampering their dry, rough and tired feet. It uplifts your feet by reviving the skin and restoring the moisture. Our disposable foot mask contains a rich blend of 10 botanical extracts and 7 antioxidants that delivers nutrition deep into your feet, giving them a hydrated and a youthful look. It helps soften your cuticles and nourishes your nails. It also increases feet's suppleness and keeps them smooth and refreshed, all in less than 30 minutes. This treatment is easy to use, effective, non messy and non sticky. It is free from any chemical and synthetic ingredient that may prove harmful to your skin. It comes in durable foil packets and is very travel friendly. Foot Hydration Socks has a patented sticker link system with a 3-layer sheet technology that allows for maximum moisture delivery. The 3-layer system consists of the following- Essence layer: Filled with serum enriched with highly specialized skin care ingredients. Moisture layer: The actual sock that holds the serum and helps the feet absorb all nutrients. Moisture cover layer: The outer layer that protects and covers the serum filled sock keeping it in direct contact with the feet. This mask is non-comedogenic, pH balanced to ~6.5 and suitable for all skin types.

Title: FLAMINGO Large Knee Support (L, Beige)
The SweatShop Strength Wraps (with Carry case) Wrist Support (Free Size, Green, Red, Black)
Description: The SweatShop Strength Wraps/ Wrist wraps offer an easy-to-adjust alternative to traditional, bulkier wrist wraps. The 37" long 3” wide straps come with a simple twist-tight design for fast,custom adjustments. So,instead of repeatedly wrapping & unwrapping your wrists from one movement to the next, you can just tighten the material for extra firm support on heavier lifts, then loosen it for a little more range of motion on the next. Whether your focus is Olympic lifting, power lifting or body building the use of quality lifting wraps can help . With better wrist support, you can train longer and experience better cumulative results over time. Traditional Velcro Wrist Wraps Vs Strength Wraps These Strength wrist wraps are designed to be used for movements like snatches, clean & jerks, push press and thrusters which gives your wrist the range of motion needed. In the aforementioned movements your wrists must be able to go into the extension position when completing those movements. The velcro type wrist wraps are geared more for the max bench or max shoulder press movements. They limit your wrist movements and with those types of exercises, wrist extension is not warranted. How to Use/ Wear The Strength Wraps 1. Grab a wrap and align it so the colored thread is facing the wrist. 2. Wrap itself around your wrist keeping the stitching inline until you reach the end of the wrap. Once you are at the end of the wrap give it a twist to tighten down the wrap. The wrap should be snug but not too tight where it cuts off your circulation. 3. Take the string and just loop it around the wrap and tuck the string under itself several times to secure the wrap. (PLEASE DO NOT PULL THE STRING TO TIGHTEN) 4. You are ready to start lifting! You can tighten and loosen by just twisting clockwise and counter clockwise to your personal preference.

Title: SD Check Codefree Glucometer
Description: SD Code free Blood Glucose Meter SD Code free. The SD Code free blood glucose meter has become popular since early 2012 amongst people with diabetes who need to buy their own test strips on account of the test strips being relatively cheap. The SD Code free is produced by SD Biosensor Inc, a diagnostic company from South Korea. Basic features - The SD Code free features a large screen. The meter is easy to use and it has memory capacity to store up to 500 readings. The test strips require a 0.9 microlitre sample of blood which is a relatively small droplet of blood. Averages markers and SD Code free software. The meter provides 7::14 and 30 day averages, allows you to include meal markers before taking readings and includes a warning if a low blood glucose result is recorded. Readings can be transferred to computer to be analysed using SD Diabetes Management Software. The software can be downloaded from the SD Biosensor website. You will also need the SD Software Communication cable which can be requested directly from SD Biosensor. The SD Code free comprises : 1 x SD Codefree Blood Glucose Meter in mmol/L::1 x Adaptable Lancing Device offering 10 different comfort settings::60 x Blood Glucose Test Strips::10 x Lancets::1 x 3V Battery Type CR2032::1 x Carrying Case::1 x SD Check Strip::Full instructions and Self test diary.

Title: Zepter PBG-902 Upper Arm Bp Monitor
Description: The Zepter PBG-902 BP monitor provides an ideal solution for keeping you updated on your blood pressure condition on a daily basis. This digital BP monitor delivers quick and precise readings enabling you to measure your blood pressure without the need to visit a clinic. With the fully automatic operation facilitated by this upper arm BP monitor, you can get your blood pressure readings with ease and efficacy. Clinically tested and validated for accuracy, this Zepter BP monitor is safe and reliable in its usage. Build This Zepter PBG-902 BP monitor has been crafted to give you an easy and comfortable measuring experience. The blood pressure monitor has two components comprising of the main unit that also houses the control panel and an easy-to-attach non-integrated cuff. The main unit accommodates a large LCD screen and simple one touch push buttons. Built for easy viewing, the LCD screen displays your systolic and diastolic pressure readings along with your pulse rates with enhanced clarity. Weighing about 450 g and measuring 129 x 133 x 60 mm in dimensions, this Zepter BP monitor is lightweight and compact. The compact body of this BP monitor enables you to carry the device even if you are on the go. This digital upper arm BP monitor comes with a comfortable cuff that fits into arm sizes ranging from 22-32 cm in diameter. You can operate this BP monitor with ease and comfort as all you have to do is, attach the cuff to your arms and press the one touch button for quick and precise readings. Performance The Zepter PBG-902 upper arm BP monitor utilizes the advanced Fuzzy Logic Technology that allows inflation and deflation of the cuff and also enables the monitor to determine the ideal cuff inflation pressure related to your systolic and diastolic pressure and arm size. This increases the speed of measurement and at the same time results in precise and genuine results. The Zepter upper arm BP monitor is capable of displaying a range of 20-300 mmHg for pressure readings and 40-200 beats/minute for pulse readings. This digital blood pressure monitor by Zepter operates at a temperature ranging from 10 to 40 degree Celsius. Storing this BP monitor is ideal at a temperature range of -10 to 50 degree Celsius. Empowered with memory feature that enables the Zepter PBG-902 to store 42 readings along with date and time, you can keep a tab on your blood pressure with ease and convenience. You can use 4 AA batteries to run this BP monitor and alternately use electricity as its power source. The batteries in this monitor are efficient and durable as it capably lasts for 250 measuring sessions. Additionally, the Auto Switch-off function in the Zepter PBG-902 BP monitor enhances your battery life as the device automatically shuts down if left idle for a prolonged period. ( Adaptor to be bought separately) .

Title: Neclife Ucontrol Hi-Low Upper Arm Bp Monitor
Description: Measuring your blood pressure is now easier than ever with this Ucontrol Hi-Low upper arm BP monitor from Neclife. Just sit back and relax in the comforts of your home and check your BP with a push of a button of this unit. Displays Blood Pressure and Heart Rate The display of this unit indicates blood pressure in the range of 0 to 300 mmHg with a measurement accuracy of ±3 mmHg. Programmed to measure pulse rate in the range of 30 to 180 beats/min, this monitor displays it with the accuracy of ±5% of reading. Comfortable Cuff The cuff features the graphic indication of its correct placement which will guide you through wearing it properly. It is automatically inflated and deflated, saving you the effort of pumping it when you need to measure your blood pressure. Memory Function This BP monitor is programmed to store a few set of readings, allowing you to keep track of your heart health. This saved history helps you better understand the trend of your blood pressure and may prove beneficial in the detection of an anomaly. Auto Power-Off and Low Battery Detection This unit runs on four AA batteries and indicates when the battery power is low, so that you can replace them with the new ones for uninterrupted measurements. The Ucontrol Hi-Low BP monitor can also be powered with a medical AC adapter.
